title: Take The Dive
lyrics:
Meomchwobeolin sumsoli ama nado moleuge
Geuttae neoleul balgyeonhan sungan
Musuhan uyeondeul-i gyeolgug neolan bada-e
Heulleodeun geosman gat-eun yegam
I will Take The Dive job-eun yogjoga oneul-eun waenji gip-eo

Singing na na na na na neoleul tteoollidaga

Ppajyeodeul-eo nan



Take The Dive

Take The Dive (Woo woo woo)

Take The Dive (Woo)

Nun-eul tteugo kkum-eul kkwo ije neolan sum-eul swieo



Nalan jag-eun sesang-i neowa majuchyeoss-eul ttae

Geuttae naege il-eonan pajang

Dan han beon-ui us-eum-i musaeghaessdeon nae mam-eul

Jeonbu muldeul-igodo namjanh-a



I will Take The Dive nachseon jolyuga oneul-eun waenji gip-eo

Singing na na na na na jamsi mangseol-idaga

Ttwieodeul-eo nan



Would you Take The Dive

Would you Take The Dive

Would you Take The Dive

Neolan bada-e nal pul-eojwo ojig neolo chaewojwo



Algo sip-eo nan neoui nun-i busin pyomyeon-e

Simhae jeopyeonkkajido Oh I



Take The Dive

Take The Dive (Woo woo woo)

Take The Dive (Woo)

Nun-eul tteugo kkum-eul kkwo (Oh I will Take The Dive)

Ije neolan sum-eul swieo
